videos.description: After Fred VanVleet hits a three to put the Raptors up four, DeMar DeRozan and LaMarcus Aldridge come up clutch in the final minutes leading the Spurs to victory.

videos.description: Patty Mills went five-of-six from three with an efficient 21 points off the bench in San Antonio's win over the Raptors.
